trans-unit.source: If "constructor" is not mentioned in "-chains-" property, it will be chained using the legacy mode: using "after" chaining, calling preamble() method before each constructor, if available, and calling postscript() after all constructors were executed. trans-unit.source: If module is a string that contains slashes, then it is interpretted as a fully resolved path (typically a result returned by require.toUrl), and url should not be provided. Since XMLHttpRequest (XHR) is used to fetch the the URL contents, only modules on the same domain of the page can use this capability. The build system can inline the cache values though, to allow for xdomain hosting.
trans-unit.target: 如果module是包含斜杠的字符串，则将其解释为完全解析的路径（通常是require.toUrl返回的结果），并且不应提供url。这是首选签名。如果module是不包含斜杠的字符串，则还必须提供url，并且使用module和url来调用 dojo.moduleUrl() 生成模块URL。不推荐使用此签名。如果指定了value，则moduleUrl的缓存值将设置为该值。否则，dojo.cache将获取moduleUrl并将其存储在其内部缓存中，并为URL返回该缓存的值。要清除缓存值，请为值传递null。由于使用XMLHttpRequest（XHR）来获取URL内容，因此只有页面同一域上的模块才能使用此功能。但是，构建系统可以内联缓存值，以允许xdomain托管。
